Fy_Celuloid
This map idea was concieved after seeing something along the same lines on one brush on a sourceforts map. I immediately set about planning the map, and figuring out how to create the REAL cel-shaded effect. This map was then born. I worked on this for only 2 or 3 hours, and it is quite small. Only mp5s are available on this map, but they all have 300 ammo. The map is non-decompilable, so no-one can steal this little trick. I know that Lost has a similar map in production, or finished, but this map was in no way copied from him. In fact, the method for achieving the outlines maybe different, as I know two ways, and I think I did the more difficult way. Well, enjoy =)

Please favourite if you like!
